{"content":[{"key":"header","data":{"content":"<span>外行学代码的优势</span>","level":1},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>外行学代码的优势就是：</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>……没有优势。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":""},"common":{}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>不要迷信自己是个被埋没了的天才，</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>即是你是，这个世间还是普遍适用天道酬勤的，不努力还是白给。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span><strong><span>费曼</span></strong></span><span>曾经讲，</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span> 只要投入足够多的时间用于思考这类艰深的问题，任何人都能成为物理学家。</span>"},"common":{"quote":true}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>可问题是一般人很难坚持投入如此多的精力去思考那么艰深的问题。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>学代码也是一样，你外行，尤其还是大龄外行，想跟人内行学得一样快是不现实的。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>如果你明确了以上的事实观点，也许还是可以发现自身的一些长处的。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>我之所以被人们称为最有智慧的人，是因为我明确地知晓自己的无知。</span>"},"common":{"quote":true}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>这句话是</span><span><strong><span>苏格拉底</span></strong></span><span>说的。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>有些人想学习代码去转行就业拿高薪，我觉得这路径对90%的人是不适合的。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>回想一下，你能吃上某一行的这碗饭，那个不是寒窗苦读，摸爬滚打，甚至卧薪尝胆才得来的，如果来个外行短期就能速成，这行门槛得多低啊？哪个门槛低的行当还能赚大钱？</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>所以放弃幻想，脚踏实地，也许你还有机会。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>第一，不要想着纯靠编程这一技能去找工作吃饭。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>第二，深入思考自己最熟悉的领域。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>第三，运用第一性原理，去发现同行还没有解决好的问题。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>第四，带着这个问题去学习，去设计自己的代码学习路径图。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>以解决问题为目的去学习，成长才是最快的，</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>成功的可能也是最大的。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}},{"key":"paragraph","data":{"content":"<span>永远坚持选择大于努力，知行合一，才能修成正果。</span>"},"common":{"quote":false}}],"typeset":"typeset-1654946506456","layout":"print","basic":{"title":"","cover":"","summary":""}}